The fix for `ragHooks.ts` line 109: Instead of passing `{ question, teamId, userId }` directly (where `teamId` and `userId` might be `undefined`), I need to build the request object conditionally:

```typescript
const req: RagQueryRequest = { question };
if (teamId !== undefined) req.teamId = teamId;


if (userId !== undefined) req.userId = userId;
await api.submitQuery(req);
```

